{"tid":909500,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"個新同事走去食24蚊餐 ，俾我地笑到佢咸！🤣","createTime":"2018-11-20T12:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T12:37:41.000Z","uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3da92eb0427d48201c624c92619ed1a930a318","tid":909500,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"話說今日有個新同事入來做野，之前唔覺意睇到佢CV寫自己住公屋。佢可能想同我地埋堆，就好主動話約我地出去食晏，然後我地話好，我就話附近有間拉麵好好食，點知佢咁唔識做，話拉麵好貴，不如食麥當勞$24餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地幾個即刻係到笑，同佢講，咁下次先一齊食啦，然後我地幾個就去咗食拉麵，見到對面間麥當勞，新同事坐係裡面食緊6件麥樂雞餐，仲要拎咗3-4包茄料，邊食邊喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期一都係帶飯算，到時同佢講帶咗飯唔出去食，廢事佢難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af516e28cb23d29eaa3a48641f21235825e857ec","tid":909500,"uid":24378,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"你食晏帶埋望遠鏡？"},{"pid":"cbb7bdfd04e08c839c092ee899a193cdf6329ede","tid":909500,"uid":61005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"b2460ecec2a3c0d110a167b34e1afb4febc8a9ef","tid":909500,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"膠都廢事畀"},{"pid":"d037c8c037ce3769707d3fb3f1648cadc7304734","tid":909500,"uid":180393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"你幫佢舐過所以知佢咸?"},{"pid":"f7e9e225083b311c5bc872c6880d4ec0ebf7fd5e","tid":909500,"uid":94148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:36:56.000Z","msg":"重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428a9d787ac28caa7f3b6295e812272e764e6b70","tid":909500,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T12:37:41.000Z